description:
🌊🎙️ Two gay boys. One beach. Zero qualifications.
Welcome to The SAT Podcast, where we talk about life, relationships, pop culture, and whatever random thought crosses our minds before the next wave hits.
If you're looking for expert advice, keep scrolling. If you're looking for laughs, chaos, and good vibes, you've found the right podcast.
